flowchart TD
  A[Task request] --> B{Category provided?}
  B -- Yes --> C[Resolve category model]
  B -- No --> D{Agent provided?}
  D -- Yes --> E[Resolve agent model]
  D -- No --> F[Use fallback/default model]
  C --> G{Model available?}
  E --> G
  F --> G
  G -- Yes --> H[dispatch promptAsync]
  G -- No --> I[apply resolver fallback]
  I --> H
  H --> J[consume session output]
